{"tid":2077550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑不滿警車阻巴士上落客　兩學生涉罵警被控","createTime":"2020-06-24T11:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:49:42.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a73c3b1b0b6d5cb9125509f987036292868942f2","tid":2077550,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"2名年僅15及16歲的學生，被指在去年聖誕節於旺角罵警，被控在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為罪，案件今（24日）在西九龍法院提訊。被告暫毋須答辯，裁判官把案件押後至8月7日，讓辯方索取文件及提供法律意見予被告，期間被告准以2000港元保釋，但需守宵禁及禁足令。<br />\n2名被告分別是15歲男生及16歲女生，2人被控於2019年12月25日，在旺角彌敦道607號外地下，在公眾地方與其他不知名人士作出喧嘩或擾亂性的行為，或使用恐嚇性、辱罵性或侮辱性的言詞，其行為相當可能會破壞社會安寧。<br />\n據了解，2名被告疑因不滿有警車停泊在巴士站，令巴士不能「埋站」上落客，於是責罵在場警察。"},{"pid":"285b5b804019007c28e305832feaf6a19262d8e7","tid":2077550,"uid":32906,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:05:22.000Z","msg":"aka 辱警罪"},{"pid":"1c4fa77281e4d9bf70afeb8481dcc781be3d709c","tid":2077550,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"仲ON9過, 係叔一燒附近講粗口個單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd0ab1762e712f035e9171dced9241ebcb74dff","tid":2077550,"uid":125026,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"特權階級、黨衛軍、皇軍"},{"pid":"d37fa842e42e98bebdabe9e90a6d6302ec3ff00b","tid":2077550,"uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"期間被告准以2000港元保釋，但需守宵禁及禁足令。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母咩"},{"pid":"21f1abf82e08669cbf1859384fdcfa698ebc786e","tid":2077550,"uid":76745,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"